show.title: Phoenix Rising
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://applinks.kukufm.com/hMAw4bWGbg1R6koP8
show.description: After a long, mysterious slumber, she awakens — disoriented but burning with a quiet, unstoppable strength. Memories of betrayal, love, and loss swirl around her as she pieces together a shattered past. As the world she once knew lies in ruins, she must rise from the ashes, reclaim her destiny, and face the powerful forces that once silenced her. "Phoenix Rising" is a hauntingly emotional microdrama about rebirth, vengeance, and hope against overwhelming darkness.
